folder: Van Sicklen St. & Gravesend Neck Rd., Brooklyn, NY
original_title: Brooklyn: Van Sicklen St. - Gravesend Neck Rd.
text:
Van Sicklen Street, north side, just west of Gravesend Neck Road, showing the old Public School No. 95. The new school is on the left.

Board of Education of the City of New York  Early 1930's
